An unsweetened, organic oat milk free from added sugars, suitable for various dietary needs.
Type of Milk Plant-based, non-dairy milk Main Ingredient: Organic oats
Ideal For Vegans and vegetarians Individuals with lactose intolerance or dairy allergies Those seeking a low-fat, cholesterol-free milk alternative Consumers preferring organic and non-GMO products
Ingredients Filtered water Organic whole oats (15%) Organic hi-oleic sunflower oil Plant-based calcium Sea salt
Storage Instructions Unopened: Store in a cool, dry place. After Opening: Refrigerate and consume within 7–10 days.
Where to buy: SM Megamall Mandaluyong City, Ayala Mall Pasig City
